"title": "5058: rest, spiritual",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5058: rest, spiritual",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>To be at rest spiritually is to find peace with God through Jesus Christ. This rest is promised to all who put their trust in God and obey him.</p>\n<h2>The human desire for spiritual rest</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:19-Lam5:22\">LAM 5:19–5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:4-Ps55:8\">PSA 55:4–55:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:25-Lam3:26\">LAM 3:25–3:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:2\">1TI 2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual rest is to be found in God alone</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28-Matt11:30\">MAT 11:28–11:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:14\">EXO 33:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:2\">PSA 23:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:12\">PSA 51:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:1-Ps62:2\">PSA 62:1–62:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:5-Ps62:8\">PSA 62:5–62:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:1-Ps91:13\">PSA 91:1–91:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:3-Isa26:4\">ISA 26:3–26:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:27\">JHN 14:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1\">ROM 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:3\">GAL 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22\">GAL 5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:20\">COL 1:20</a></p>\n<h2>God promises his people spiritual rest</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:9-Heb4:11\">HEB 4:9–4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:3\">PSA 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:7\">PSA 37:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:7\">PSA 116:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:165\">PSA 119:165</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps125:1\">PSA 125:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps131:1-Ps131:3\">PSA 131:1–131:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:25\">PRO 29:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:15\">ISA 30:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:17-Isa32:18\">ISA 32:17–32:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:11\">ISA 58:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:16\">JER 6:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:7-Jer17:8\">JER 17:7–17:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1\">JHN 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:6\">ROM 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:4\">1PE 3:4</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual rest is not for the wicked</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:4-Ps1:5\">PSA 1:4–1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:10\">PSA 112:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:23\">ECC 2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:22\">ISA 48:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:20-Isa57:21\">ISA 57:20–57:21</a></p>\n<h2>God's offer of rest rejected by a faithless people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:12\">ISA 28:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:16\">JER 6:16</a></strong></p>",
